cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG 

The paper deals with generating RGB images from depth data, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The focus is on face-to-face translation, which falls under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The proposed method uses deep learning techniques, which are often associated with artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
